title: Build Your Running Body: A Total-Body Fitness Plan
description:
Build Your Running Body: A Total-Body Fitness Plan for All Distance Runners, from Milers to UltramarathonersRun Farther, Faster, and Injury-Free by Pete Magill, Thomas Schwartz, Melissa Breyer

With the breakthrough whole-body training program in Build Your Running Body, runners will improve their times, run longer and more comfortably, and reduce injury
